<item>
            <title>[LU-17623] sanity-scrub: ASSERTION(debug_buf == string_buf) failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17623</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Aur&#233;lien Degr&#233;mont &amp;lt;adegremont@nvidia.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b030b54c-d084-4259-999d-c05e01d09f23&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b030b54c-d084-4259-999d-c05e01d09f23&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/102884&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/102884&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-477.27.1.el8_8.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/102884&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/102884&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-477.27.1.el8_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;libcfs/libcfs/tracefile.c:673:libcfs_debug_msg()) ASSERTION(debug_buf == string_buf) failed

